reviewText: I bought his edition of Tom & Jerry as a gift, but got to see a few of the episodes for myself. The DVD is of high quality. The cartoons are classics and will never go out of style. They just don't make 'em like this anymore. I feel a bit silly writing a review for a cartoon series that has withstood the test of time. Everyone's heard of Tom & Jerry. Every episode is a gem; no a single lemon in the bunch.
